name: Abhishek Kumar
note:
updated
 looking for animator or explainer video creator.

Сompany Name: Nanogence SA,(Research) - http://www.nanogence.com/

We interviewed:
Anton - https://rh-s.com/video-editors/anton-s/ very communicative, put questions, give suggestions showed his works.
Artem - https://rh-s.com/video-editors/artem-y/ showed his works, had some problems with connection, but presented himself well.
Aleksandr - https://rh-s.com/video-editors/oleksandr-v/ showed his works, answered the questions.
Natalia -   https://rh-s.com/video-editors/nataliia-t/ was the best one in her knowledge, showed her works.

Result:
Abhishek is sure that any of these guys are able to do his task, he will talk to his colleague to choose the best animation style and come to me by tomorrow, so then we can start on Monday.
Contact Person: Abhishek Kumar,(Founder,CEO)

Country - Location: Switzerland.

Product: Road, mining, cement production, tunnels, oil & gas and automation, chemical, Sustainbility, Energy storage, Construction materials, and Pharmaceuticals

Target Audience: Construction markets, Manufacturing Companies.

Immediate Requirement: Video Animator. They have a Startup project. They need to create an animation for their website, to explain the proposition about the product to client. It should be 4-5 short ( 30 sec-1 min) video .The person they need should be an expert in video creation (animation creation). They're not sure they need a long time cooperation, probably it will be 2 weeks ( 8 hours per day).

Future need: UI Developer. ( For a longer cooperation)

Next Step: Interview with candidates.

Next Contact Date: Tomorrow 03.04.21. 10 AM (our time)

name: Cedric Séguéla
note:
Can you please give me an overview of what does the lead generation manager does?
Company Name: Qualizy
Company Website: https://www.qualizy.fr/ 
http://www.secretsdecuisine.fr/
Contact Person: Cedric Seguela
Results:
We have interviewed candidates for Cedric for the position of sales manager at unfortunately he didn't like anybody. They all didn't have enough experience in presenting and selling software.
So I will come to him as soon as we will find somebody great.

Product:The company  helps food businesses and restaurants streamline their food safety records processes.
Qualizy is changing the way people work towards compliance and documentation by automating the process.
They do everything to make it easier to monitor.
Cendric wants candidates who speaks English fluently and help to lead out ghost their business.
He needs to attract more clients.
Country- Location: France
Target Audience: For businesses which are involved with food, either restaurants,  manufacturers, or retail businesses of any size. 
Immediate Requirement: LG manager who speaks English fluently.
He/she needs to attract potential clients on Linkedin and create a list of them, create events and later when the manager will be aware of business to  make a call from the company's script.
Next Step: Sending CVs of candidates who are good for him.
Next Contact Date: Cedric will write the date on email, when we can set up an intetrview this week

name: Vidspice
note:
Join the online meeting with Remote Helpers in Ukraine to uncover new pathways for maximizing the potential of Vidspice team and resources.


Website: rh-s.com

Company website: https://www.vidspice.be

Company info:  VidSpice is a video production company focused on creating affordable and engaging videos for businesses, with a straightforward pricing model starting from €290. They emphasize the value of concise, attention-grabbing content, noting that most videos on social media are watched for only about 8 seconds, making shorter videos of 15-30 seconds more effective than longer ones. VidSpice aims to simplify the video production process for companies, offering a hassle-free experience with no hidden fees, delivering a finished video within two weeks of collaboration.

Comments: Hannes De Wandele

(https://www.linkedin.com/in/hannes-de-wandele-73a73b143/)

 We would like to test 10 free hours, we need a video editor.
Country-Location: Maldegem, Flemish Region, Belgium

Manager: Korzhova Liudmyla

need_candidates.comment_requirements:
Professional skills: Video editing, color grading, adding transitions, potentially adding subtitles in Dutch or French, adhering to specific client branding and style.

Software: Monday (CRM tool for project management also was interested in ours)

Responsibilities: Checking document requirements, editing videos, uploading finished videos on Drive, possibly adding subtitles in Dutch or French as needed.

30-40 videos per month to 50-60
